node.title: Energy Minister Dan van Holst Pellekaan unveiled as SA's new Deputy Premier
node.alt: A tall man in a checked white shirt sits on a park bench in a park covered in green grass with a playground in the background
node.description: Dan van Holst Pellekaan is officiallyÂ South Australia's new Deputy Premier, after a vote of Lower House Liberal MPs this afternoon.
node.content: ["Dan van Holst Pellekaan is officially\u00a0South Australia's new Deputy Premier, after a vote of Lower House Liberal MPs this afternoon.", "That's despite getting sworn into the job on Tuesday, as an interim measure following Vickie Chapman's resignation.", "Ms Chapman handed her resignation to Premier Steven Marshall on Sunday afternoon, because the Ombudsman is investigating her decision to block a port development on Kangaroo Island.", "More to come.\u00a0"]
